### ===========================
### Courses API Tests
### ===========================

### 1. Create a new course CS101
POST http://localhost:3000/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CS101",
  "name": "Intro to CS"
}

### 2. Create another course CS102
POST http://localhost:3000/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CS102",
  "name": "Data Structures"
}

### 3. Attempt to create course with missing name (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CS103"
}

### 4. Get all courses
GET http://localhost:3000/courses

### ==================================================================
### Reviews API Tests
### ==================================================================

### 5. Add a review to CS101
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "difficulty": 4,
  "hoursPerWeek": 10
}

### 6. Add another review to CS101
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "difficulty": 5,
  "hoursPerWeek": 12
}

### 7. Add a review to CS102
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 2,
  "difficulty": 3,
  "hoursPerWeek": 8
}

### 8. Attempt to add review with missing fields (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "difficulty": 3
}

### 9. Attempt to add review with difficulty > 5 (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "difficulty": 6,
  "hoursPerWeek": 8
}

### 10. Attempt to add review for nonexistent course (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 999,
  "difficulty": 3,
  "hoursPerWeek": 5
}

### ====================================================================
### Course Stats Tests
### ====================================================================

### 11. Get stats for CS101 (should show avgDifficulty ~4.5, avgHours ~11, reviewCount 2)
GET http://localhost:3000/courses/1/stats

### 12. Get stats for CS102 (should show avgDifficulty 3, avgHours 8, reviewCount 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/courses/2/stats

### 13. Get stats for a course with no reviews (CS103)
GET http://localhost:3000/courses/3/stats